Name: scriptTextFont

Type: property

Syntax: set the scriptTextFont to <fontName> 

Summary: Deprecated and will be removed in a future release.

Introduced: 1.0

OS: mac,windows,linux

Platforms: desktop,server,web

Description:
The <scriptTextFont> property is present in LiveCode for compatibility with scripts imported from HyperCard and should not be used in new code. It will be removed entirely in a future release.
